LOCUS       PT5_lacO                  81 bp    DNA              UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  PT5/lacO is the bacteriophage-T5 sigma-70 promoter flanked by two
            lac operators, giving lacI-repressible, IPTG-inducible transcription
            (the pQE/Bujard expression module)..
